__

17:55.875 --> 17:57.642
(Laughs)

17:57.677 --> 17:58.910
Well, that's a relief.

18:03.566 --> 18:06.551
This place... bad.

18:07.653 --> 18:10.322
Ride home?

18:10.356 --> 18:12.491
No. Thank you.

18:16.295 --> 18:20.165
No, actually. I'm not.

18:20.199 --> 18:23.935
I've had a really crappy night.

18:23.970 --> 18:25.070
I don't fit in anywhere.

18:25.104 --> 18:27.038
Not at home, not at school,

18:27.073 --> 18:29.007
and now I'm rambling to some hot, deaf guy

18:29.041 --> 18:30.609
who's probably going to dismember me

18:30.643 --> 18:31.777
and throw me into a shallow grave.

18:33.679 --> 18:37.516
Not dismember me.

18:37.550 --> 18:39.618
And now we know you can read lips.

18:45.658 --> 18:47.225
What the hell?

18:47.260 --> 18:48.527
I live in Mission Hills.

19:01.023 --> 19:04.776
Uh, better safe than sorry, I guess.

19:16.787 --> 19:17.987
<i>(Hip-hop music playing)
* try to come up with your own thing, yeah *</i>

19:18.005 --> 19:19.606
<i>* come alive... *</i>

