<i>(Vocalizes)</i>

19:22.126 --> 19:23.960
We keep running into each other.

19:23.995 --> 19:25.962
Yeah.

19:26.147 --> 19:28.882
It's a great party.

19:28.766 --> 19:29.833
Yeah, it's okay.

19:33.404 --> 19:34.654
Do you want to go up to your room?

19:34.689 --> 19:38.475
<i>(Man rapping)</i>

19:47.151 --> 19:50.086
<i>Man: Don't go.</i>

19:49.751 --> 19:51.618
Don't you have important state business

19:51.653 --> 19:52.819
to attend to, Senator?

19:52.854 --> 19:54.588
(Groans)

19:54.622 --> 19:56.556
Yes.

19:56.591 --> 19:58.659
But I'd much rather
stay here and ravish you

19:58.693 --> 20:00.560
like "The Falconer's Mmistress."

20:00.595 --> 20:01.828
(Laughs)

20:01.863 --> 20:03.530
Very funny.

20:03.564 --> 20:05.432
- (Moans)
- (Giggles)

20:05.466 --> 20:07.301
Speaking of... so... 

20:07.335 --> 20:09.603
the character of Manuel,

20:09.637 --> 20:12.239
is he based on me?

20:12.273 --> 20:13.373
Maybe.

20:13.408 --> 20:17.311
Oh... aren't you afraid
John might suspect something?

20:17.345 --> 20:19.146
No.

20:19.180 --> 20:22.015
He never gets around to reading 'em.

20:24.118 --> 20:26.053
Well, he doesn't know what he's missing.

