(Engine quiets)

20:54.515 --> 20:56.350
Well, thank you.

20:58.586 --> 21:00.153
Thank you.

21:03.491 --> 21:06.193
Oh, yeah. Yeah, I... I paint.

21:10.031 --> 21:12.099
Camera?

21:12.133 --> 21:14.101
Pictures? Oh... photography.

21:17.038 --> 21:19.906
Well, uh... 

21:19.941 --> 21:22.709
tomorrow you can come back here,

21:22.744 --> 21:25.846
and I could show you some of my paintings.

21:25.880 --> 21:29.649
And you could show me
some of your photography.

21:32.487 --> 21:33.653
I'm assuming that's a yes?

21:35.723 --> 21:38.158
Yes.

21:42.497 --> 21:44.030
(Starts engine)

21:48.236 --> 21:50.303
Yes!

22:33.314 --> 22:35.449
(Sighs)

