Yeah, I... I stayed up
late learning a few signs.

25:04.472 --> 25:07.374
<i>We don't look alike.</i>

25:07.408 --> 25:11.311
Yeah, she's not really my sister.

25:11.346 --> 25:14.548
It's a long story.

25:14.582 --> 25:17.250
I keep drawing pictures

25:17.285 --> 25:21.988
of what I imagine my real mom to look like.

25:22.023 --> 25:23.190
Like, does she have my hair?

25:23.224 --> 25:25.125
Or my eyes?

25:25.159 --> 25:26.793
I pass people on the street,

25:26.828 --> 25:29.162
and I keep thinking,

25:29.197 --> 25:30.864
"that could be her."

25:33.034 --> 25:34.634
Oh! I remember this one.

25:34.669 --> 25:35.869
Ah... oh, find!

25:35.903 --> 25:37.904
Find. I've tried.

25:37.938 --> 25:41.708
(Sighs) But my parents
won't talk about her.

25:44.879 --> 25:47.748
List?

25:47.782 --> 25:48.815
Papers! Yeah.

25:48.850 --> 25:50.584
I figured there had to be
something from the trial,

25:50.618 --> 25:54.454
