25:56.607 --> 25:59.393
Box... turning, turning a door.

25:59.427 --> 26:01.361
Like a tiny house.

26:01.396 --> 26:03.430
Like a lock... a safe, a safe!

26:03.448 --> 26:06.199
Ah! I'm getting good.

26:06.234 --> 26:08.135
We don't have a safe.

26:08.169 --> 26:10.237
Ah... 

