but there's one in the car wash.

26:26.020 --> 26:27.754
Uh, the combination?

26:27.789 --> 26:30.657
It's probably one of my
dad's old baseball stats.

26:30.691 --> 26:33.510
So... no.

26:33.561 --> 26:35.495
What the hell are you doing here?

26:35.530 --> 26:38.432
<i>What the hell are you doing here?</i>

26:38.466 --> 26:40.267
Just a little poker game.

26:40.301 --> 26:42.402
With the Sons of Anarchy?

26:44.205 --> 26:45.272
Who's he?

