A friend.

26:54.348 --> 26:56.883
He was asking who you are.

26:56.918 --> 26:59.119
Why doesn't he talk?

26:59.153 --> 27:01.788
- He's deaf.
- So you and your deaf buddy

27:01.767 --> 27:03.601
