27:07.572 --> 27:08.773
Well, that's not where he keeps that stuff.

27:08.807 --> 27:10.708
You know where he keeps that stuff?

27:12.411 --> 27:13.611
<i>Toby, unless you want dad to find out</i>

27:13.645 --> 27:15.413
about whatever's going on in there,

27:15.447 --> 27:17.314
