Why didn't you tell me?

27:34.166 --> 27:35.933
You know how it is.

27:35.967 --> 27:38.869
Everybody tries to forget
any of that every happened.

27:45.010 --> 27:46.710
<i>Bay, this is going to take forever.</i>

27:46.745 --> 27:48.479
(Sighs)

27:51.616 --> 27:53.484
Dad.

27:55.554 --> 27:56.754
Those are my parents.

27:59.291 --> 28:01.425
You... you... oh...

28:01.460 --> 28:03.360
your parents.

28:08.266 --> 28:11.001
Separate... separated... oh, they divorced.

28:10.986 --> 28:13.220
Your parents divorced.

28:13.255 --> 28:16.123
Chicken dance?

28:16.158 --> 28:18.225
Oh, accordion. Accordion.

28:18.260 --> 28:20.761
Okay, so, your parents divorced

28:20.796 --> 28:22.696
and the court papers

28:22.731 --> 28:24.031
were in an accordion.

28:26.067 --> 28:29.537
Okay, it's like sections... 

28:29.571 --> 28:30.955
oh, like... oh, an accordion folder.

28:31.006 --> 28:32.473
So that's what we're looking for.

28:32.507 --> 28:34.675
We're looking for an accordion folder.

28:34.709 --> 28:37.411
Uh... let's see.

28:37.429 --> 28:40.548
I don't know why we have so many boas.

28:47.656 --> 28:49.390
Oh! There it is.

28:49.424 --> 28:51.091
Okay.

28:51.126 --> 28:53.394
Uh... custody agreement.

28:55.464 --> 28:57.398
Restraining order?

29:04.139 --> 29:06.841
These are letters she sent to Daphne.

29:21.790 --> 29:23.724
And to me.

29:46.915 --> 29:49.016
She wanted me.

30:05.817 --> 30:07.635
What are you doing?

30:07.669 --> 30:10.671
Just giving some stuff away.

30:10.705 --> 30:13.440
What are those?

30:13.475 --> 30:15.442
Letters from Regina.

30:15.477 --> 30:16.544
Who?

30:16.578 --> 30:17.511
You know... 

30:17.546 --> 30:19.313
my other mom.

30:19.347 --> 30:22.283
Your other mom.

30:22.317 --> 30:24.184
You want to see them?

30:27.135 --> 30:29.670
She was my mom for, like, two seconds.

30:29.704 --> 30:31.005
And it was all a big mistake anyway.

30:32.974 --> 30:34.942
There are dozens of letters.

30:34.976 --> 30:36.544
Birthday cards,

30:36.578 --> 30:38.679
references to Christmas
gifts that she sent you.

30:38.713 --> 30:41.449
She thought of herself as your mom.

30:44.586 --> 30:46.320
Where did you get those?

30:46.354 --> 30:49.223
In the guest house. Hidden.

30:50.492 --> 30:53.127
I'm sure there's a reason
that they didn't show us.

30:53.161 --> 30:55.262
Whatever. All I know is

30:55.297 --> 30:57.164
they put a restraining order on her.

30:57.199 --> 30:59.266
Threatening that if she
ever contacted us directly,

30:59.301 --> 31:01.001
