32:59.885 --> 33:01.051
That we were connecting.

33:01.086 --> 33:02.820
Oh, please.

33:02.854 --> 33:04.855
Are you going to tell me
now that he listens to you?

33:04.890 --> 33:07.124
He does.

33:07.158 --> 33:10.828
