33:18.837 --> 33:21.372
Like with Daphne?

33:21.406 --> 33:24.275
When I wanted us to learn sign language?

33:24.309 --> 33:25.576
You shut that down right away.

33:25.610 --> 33:27.444
Are you going to go
back to that? Seriously?

33:27.479 --> 33:29.346
Putting her in a deaf bubble?

33:29.381 --> 33:31.181
